item.description:
Join me for a few hours of fun playing disc golf and hiking the trails out at Muldoon park. For the newbies, basically we toss Frisbee like discs at metal baskets along trails in the woods. It's alot of fun and we don't keep score. For those who haven't been back in the last 2 weeks, they have lengthened all the holes. Please bring long pants, good shoes, water, bug spray and your smiles. We will meet at the Hillside store to pick up the discs. there is no charge.

Here's a link to the site

http://www.dgcoursereview.com/reviews.php?id=1588&mode=r

Any questions..603-315-0275  Cindy

 

Rain will cancel this meetup.
item.how_to_find_us: we'll meet at the store across from the park to pick up discs
